<div class="subpages-banner">
  <h1>CALCULATOR</h1>
</div>

<div class="calculator-title-container">
  <p> We are here to help you understand how much you are owed and reclaim what's legally yours!</p>
  <div class="line"></div>
  <h1>Calculate your payments</h1>

</div class="d-flex justify-content-evenly">
  <div class="calculator-container">
    <div class="row g-3 ms-5">
      <div class="calculator-section-container col-6">
      <h3 class="calculator-subtitle">Input your information</h3>
        <%= render "form", calculation: @calculation %>
      </div>
      <div class= "col-md-5 col-lg-4 order-md-last">
        <% if controller.action_name == "new"%>
          <div class="card  my-5 ms-5 rounded  shadow-sm border-secondary" style="width: 22rem;">
            <div class="card-header">
              <p class="fw-bold pt-3 ms-2">Fill The Form To Calculate...</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
              <li class="list-group-item p-3 ms-2 text-muted">Vacation compensation ...</li>
              <li class="list-group-item p-3 ms-2 text-muted">Christmas bonus ...</li>
              <li class="list-group-item p-3 ms-2 text-muted">Unpaid working days ...</li>
              <li class="list-group-item p-3 ms-2 text-muted">compensation ...</li>
              <li class="list-group-item p-3 ms-2 text-muted">total ...</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        <% else %>
          <h3 class= "calculator-subtitle ">The settlement you are entitled to is:</h3>
          <% if @calculation.valid? %>
            <%= render "show", calculation: @calculation %>
          <% else %>
            <%= @calculation.errors.full_messages %>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="calculator-disclaimer-container p-3 text-center text-muted">
  <p>
      Disclaimer: The displayed ammount is an estimate
      and should no be considered a legal advice, consult
      with a lawyer for more information.
    </p>
  </div>

  <hr class="calculator-section-break-line">

  <div class="calculator-explanation-container container-md text-center">
    <h1>Steps to calculate your severance payment</h1>
    <div class="line-container">
    <div class="line"></div>
    </div>

<br>

      <p class = "my-3">
        To calculate your severance enter the following Information.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>The day you started working.</li>
        <li>Your last day at work.</li>
        <li>Your monthly salary.</li>
        <li>The cause of termination, that could be
        resignation or either justified or unjustified dismissal.
        </li>
        <li>Your christmas bonus, yo should know according the law the mini
        mum has to be 15 days.</li>
      </ul>

<br>

    <h2 class = "text-center ">Information</h2>
      <p class = "my-3">
       The calculator will compute an estimated result with the information provided.
       It will give you a result broken down by sections that will be:
       <ul>
          <li>Vacation compensation: the ammount owed for the vacation days that you have not taken.</li>
          <li>Christmas bonus: the ammount owed to the christmas bonus proportional to the days worked in the present year.</li>
          <li>Unpaid working days: the ammount owed for the days that you worked if your last day is before your payment day.</li>
          <li>Termination compensation: If your employer fires you without a cause you are entitled to a compensation equal to 3 months of salary.</li>
       </ul>
      The ammount is an estimation and should not be considered a legal advice, you should consult a professional.
      </p>
  </div>
</div>
